&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated quantitative researcher to join our Investment Management &amp;amp; Research group, focussing on MENA Equities. You will play a key role in researching, developing and operating our equities strategies in the region, partnering with portfolio managers, researchers, and technology to build and optimise the full strategy lifecycle – from research and back testing to live trading and risk management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will spend an initial period of approximately 6 months working in our London office before relocating to our office in Abu Dhabi.&lt;/p&gt;
