&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of professional software development experience, ideally in financial services or data-intensive systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong backend capability in C#/.NET - you are comfortable designing services, APIs, and data integrations, not just consuming them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competent with a modern frontend framework - you can build UIs that non-technical users actually want to use&lt;/li&gt;
